thought.text: Great! Now let me get the complete results ordered by price difference:

data.query:
SELECT 
  `Product Name`,
  `Our Price`,
  `Competitor Price`,
  `Price Difference`,
  CASE 
    WHEN `Price Difference` > 0 THEN 'We are MORE expensive'
    WHEN `Price Difference` < 0 THEN 'We are LESS expensive'
    ELSE 'Same price'
  END as Competitive_Position
FROM `bigquery_pricing_analysis.analysis` 
ORDER BY `Price Difference` DESC
